      "text": "And I brought the gold pieces, little gold pieces.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "And he know [INAUDIBLE] the doctor told me to come to see about this guy, [INAUDIBLE] the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "Yes, I feel [INAUDIBLE] with my brother will be for us better to go over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "This was in the city.",
